  "body": {
    "comment": "Cardano憲法v2.3では多くの整理が行われましたが、\n特に重要な変更は次の3点です。\nBudget Info Actionの廃止と全件監査の義務化\n　一部の大きな支出だけでなく、すべてのトレジャリー引き出しを監査対象とし、透明性を強化。\n提案文書の不変性（immutability）の明文化\n　投票中に内容を変更できないよう固定化し、信頼性を保証。\n非拘束的な期待・推奨条項の削除\n　助言的な条文を削除し、実効性あるルールだけを残して明確化。\nv2.3は、「ルールを簡潔にし、誰もが同じ条件で、信頼できる形でガバナンスに参加できる」改訂です。\nこれら三つの合理的な変更を支持し、Yesで投票します。\n\n—\n\nCardano Constitution v2.3 introduces several refinements,\nbut the three most significant updates are:\nRemoval of the Budget Info Action and universal audit requirement\nAll treasury withdrawals, not just large ones, are now subject to equal auditing for greater transparency.\nCodification of proposal immutability\nProposals can no longer be altered during voting, ensuring integrity and trust.\nDeletion of non-binding expectation and encouragement clauses\nRemoved advisory language to keep only enforceable, practical rules.\nv2.3 is a reform that simplifies the rules and enables everyone to participate in governance under equal and trustworthy conditions.\nI support the rationality of these three changes and vote Yes."
  },
